---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions | OneStopSite 88x31 Button Maker"
  description="Review the terms and conditions for using OneStopSite. Understand guidelines for custom graphics creation, licenses, and webmaster use."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-0 pb-12 px-4">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-900 pb-8 mb-10 text-center sm:text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950 text-xs text-emerald-400 mb-4 font-mono">
        <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span>LEGAL POLICY</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight font-sans">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-base">Last updated: June 18, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-neutral-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using the <strong class="text-white font-semibold">OneStopSite 88x31 Button Editor</strong>, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms &amp; Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must cease using our services immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">2. Use of the Editor</h2>
        <p>
          Our application is designed to help users create 88x31 pixel art badges, retro buttons, neocities templates, and personal web graphics.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-3 pl-0">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>You are granted a non-exclusive, revocable, worldwide license to use the editor for personal, indie, and commercial projects.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>You may upload custom images, edit layer values, add frame delays, and compile animated GIFs.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>You are solely responsible for ensuring you have the legal right to use any images, icons, or assets you upload to the canvas.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">3. Creative License and Ownership</h2>
        <p>
          We do not claim ownership of the graphics or badges you produce. All buttons, animations, and icons created using OneStopSite belong to you.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are free to share, copy, modify, distribute, or display your custom buttons on personal sites, neocities profiles, geocities directories, or commercial blogs without attribution to OneStopSite, though a retro link exchange back to us is always appreciated!
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">4. Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <p>
          You agree not to use the editor to create content that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-3 pl-0">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>Is illegal, harmful, threatening, abusive, or promotes hate speech.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>Infringes on the intellectual property, copyright, trademark, or privacy rights of any third party.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-mono select-none mt-1.5">•</span>
            <span>Attempts to inject malicious code, attack our domain, or disrupt site performance.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          OneStopSite is provided on an "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" basis. We make no warranties or representations, express or implied, regarding the reliability, uptime, accuracy, or suitability of the editor.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not guarantee that the editor will be completely error-free or that saved templates in your LocalStorage will persist indefinitely. We highly recommend exporting your layout templates as JSON files to secure your progress.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          In no event shall OneStopSite, its founders, or contributors be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages resulting from the use or inability to use our site editor, even if advised of the possibility of such damages.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">7. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms &amp; Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws applicable to internet utility tools, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
